 wholly in harmony with </div><div class="t m45a x21 h11 y482 ff2 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">His character. </div><div class="t m2a6 x43 h11 y483 ff2 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Christ is now dealing with the sin </div><div class="t m45b x21 h11 y484 ff2 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">problem in the most holy place of </div><div class="t m45c x21 h11 y485 ff2 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the heavenly sanctuary. This work </div><div class="t m45d x21 h11 y486 ff2 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">will soon be finished. He will then </div><div class="t m45e x21 h11 y487 ff2 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">confront sin on its home grounds. </div><div class="t m45f x21 h11 y488 ff2 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Heaven will release its unmixed fury </div><div class="t m460 x21 h11 y489 ff2 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">on the heads of the unsaved. The </div><div class="t m461 x21 h11 y48a ff2 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">rebellion will be stamped out. Sin </div><div class="t m351 x21 h11 y48b ff2 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">must be eradicated. Christ must </div><div class="t m462 x21 h11 y48c ff2 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">come! </div><div class="t m463 x21 h22 y48d ff1 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">DAILY HIGHLIGHTS </div><div class="t m258 x21 h22 y48e ff1 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. </div><div class="t m464 x9a h22 y48e ff1 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;And Receive You&quot; </div><div class="t m170 x9a h22 y4d ff1 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(John 14:3; 2 Peter 3:10) </div><div class="t m60 x21 h22 y48f ff1 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t m465 x9a h22 y48f ff1 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Distress of Nations&quot; </div><div class="t m466 x9a h22 y490 ff1 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Luke </div><div class="t m467 xbf h11 y491 ff2 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">21:25, 26) </div><div class="t m1e8 x21 h22 y1a7 ff1 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t m468 x9a h22 y1a8 ff1 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Defiled Earth </div><div class="t m3ad x9a h22 y492 ff1 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Isa. 24:5, 6) </div><div class="t m25f x21 h22 y493 ff1 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4. </div><div class="t m3